{"tid":2501444,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"後生到成個阿伯咁","createTime":"2021-04-23T11:06:30.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-23T11:19:07.000Z","uid":388649,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"73d9774dd17d7117a000bd059953ac48a52febac","tid":2501444,"uid":388649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-23T11:06:30.000Z","msg":"有冇人好似我咁 <br />\n二十幾歲仲讀緊書 但係咩都唔想煩<br />\n明明係大好青春 但係覺得拍拖好煩唔想拍<br />\n有時出街又覺得要諗點同人傾計又唔想出<br />\n得閒個陣就留係屋企自己打下機 睇下片<br />\n成二十幾歲就好似啲退休阿伯咁 一個識用科技既阿伯<br />\n過住啲休休閒閒毫無激情既日子 <br />\n咩都唔想煩 只想每日舒舒服服度過<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n雖然好想轉換下心態 但係點都轉唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b0bf67d66633877fa8059cbac76a5c1fe850deb8","tid":2501444,"uid":307927,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-23T11:09:45.000Z","msg":"只係你溝唔正女焗住改變心態心境令自己好過d姐"},{"pid":"93740bafaee3a7c00a2e089dac31989775709ae9","tid":2501444,"uid":325243,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-23T11:10:59.000Z","msg":"開始感覺到自己可以破處<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2346022\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2346022</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n樓主溝唔到女 之後睇破紅塵"},{"pid":"1f42e7a1129725efb78980444774c9e0bc8933a6","tid":2501444,"uid":314828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b0bf67d66633877fa8059cbac76a5c1fe850deb8","tid":2501444,"uid":307927,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-23T11:09:45.000Z","msg":"只係你溝唔正女焗住改變心態心境令自己好過d姐"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-23T11:11:02.000Z","msg":"唔好踢爆人"},{"pid":"c15db30c6e85e434e5a911a62c35faa7475a922a","tid":2501444,"uid":78243,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"202